    • getLibraryMemberFormId

      public LibraryMember getLibraryMemberFormId(String id)
      Searches for a library member by their ID. The method checks first among users, then among admins. If a matching member is found, it is returned; otherwise, null is returned.
      Parameters:
      id - the ID of the library member to search for.
      Returns:
      the LibraryMember with the specified ID, or null if no match is found.
